  "time_ut": 1656649440,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d8b\u0d9a\u0dc3\u0dca \u0d86\u0dba\u0dad\u0db1\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0d9a\u0ddd\u0da7\u0dd2 03\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0d85\u0db0\u0dd2\u0d9a \u0dbb\u0db1\u0dca \u0d89\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dc3\u0dd4 04\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dcf\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd4",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "04 gold prawns worth over Rs. 30 million seized from a pawning institution",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Four people, including a woman, have been arrested by the Norwegian Police and the Hatton Divisional Crime Branch for allegedly stealing 1 1/2 kilos of jewelery worth Rs. 15 million from a jewelery pawn shop in Norwood yesterday (30).",
        "The robbery took place on December 9 last year and one of the suspects was found buried in the backyard of his Norwood Venture Estate home without selling the stolen jewelery, police said.",
        "Regarding the related theft, the police have taken fingerprints from several people and have conducted further investigations. The Norwood police initially arrested two people based on the matching of the relevant fingerprints. From their questioning, the police have managed to arrest a fifty-year-old woman and another person who worked at the related mortgage center.",
        "Among the gold jewelery found by the suspects were 54 gold necklaces, 757 gold earrings, 177 gold pendants, 404 gold rings, 84 gold trusses, 01 gold bracelet, 09 gold pieces and a total weight of 1484 grams. 1 1/2 kilos, police said.",
        "The Hatton Senior Superintendent of Police said that the main suspect in the case had been working at the pawning center for about 10 years. Mr. said.",
        "The suspects are said to be residents of the Norwood area and are between the ages of 35 and 50 and will be produced before the Hatton Magistrate's Court today (01).",
        "Investigations into the theft were carried out under the supervision of Hatton SSP Vijitha Alwis."
      ],
